### Before Any Changes

```bash
npm run validate:layout
```

### Protected Files

- `index.html` (CSS order)
- `styles/meds.css`
- `styles/guidelines.css`
- `pages/meds.js`
- `pages/guidelines.js`

### After Changes

```bash
npm run validate:layout
npm run security:check
```

### If Validation Fails

1. Check `docs/LAYOUT_PROTECTION.md`
2. Review recent changes: `git log --oneline -- styles/ pages/`
3. Hard refresh browser (Ctrl+Shift+R)

### Test Routes

- `/` - Main page
- `/#/meds` - Medications (grid layout)
- `/#/guidelines` - Guidelines (sidebar + tabs)

